            "text": "A New Chapter",
            "heading_tag": "h1",
            "text_color": "#000000",
            "gradient": ""
          }
        },
        "richtext_QfCC7x": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>What Riley and I started as a shared dream — two sisters from New York City — became something we could have never imagined.</p><p>A place where women feel comfortable, confident, and completely themselves. That was always our vision. And it still is.</p><p>And now… because of you, we're growing. I'm moving Claire & Riley to a bigger home — a new space, with the same heart I pour into every single piece.</p><p>To celebrate this special moment, I'm offering exclusive moving sale savings of <strong>up to 70% off</strong> our most-loved styles. A chance to take a piece of our story with you, before I step into what's next.</p><p>I produce every collection in limited quantities — once they're gone, they won't return.</p><p>Thank you for being part of this journey. It means everything to me. 🤍</p><p><em>With love,<br/>Claire — Claire & Riley, New York City</em></p>"
          }
        }
      },
